{"tid":1414520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港反送中越演越烈  柯P預言：將蔓延到廣州","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:07.000Z","uid":35790,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2664affc4bfadbb14b8d34364438ed59883ca4d1","tid":1414520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"香港反送中越演越烈 柯P預言：將蔓延到廣州<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-05<br />\n<br />\n〔記者沈佩瑤／台北報導〕香港反送中越演越烈，今天更發動全港罷工、罷市、罷課等「大三罷」行動，不僅交通陷入癱瘓，港股也因此受挫。<br />\n<br />\n台北市長柯文哲今早受訪被問及看法時表示，自己講過很多遍，香港現在和2013年、2014年的台灣一樣，民怨沒有解決，就是今天這裡抗議，明天那裡抗議，北京政府也會擔憂，如果香港一直鬧下去，有可能會蔓延到廣州。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柯強調，這也是很誠實的問題，經濟、社會發展不會永遠維持這麼大的落差，要一黨專政很困難。<br />\n<br />\n他孩提到，就像台灣，民國60年的時候「台灣錢淹腳目」，所以人民對政府的滿意度很高啊，但等到有錢的時候，就會開始想說，那為什麼台北市長不能民選，總統不能直選，所以經濟發展到一定程度，政治要求就會提高。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲說，香港的GDP比台灣來得高，卻沒有像台灣這麼自由，一定會出問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2874446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2874446&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=60c29e56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2874446&h=9193d35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2874446</a>"},{"pid":"b4711daeded8eafed72d5d5fc6953ef9a9e1b3e5","tid":1414520,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3471ae67a6551dd70963ea8e79e03a05547e1857","tid":1414520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cff32f626632754e71b6e9ff137fbda2a217bfc","tid":1414520,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺會囉"},{"pid":"5be8b429694c0e241572c626950ec66bc2e8ccda","tid":1414520,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96148d00f43780b615da222007df4b880f26e7be","tid":1414520,"uid":2558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"深圳都上唔撚到啦"},{"pid":"61d9134f99e01e0d5babf228c3cf98d337823135","tid":1414520,"uid":54303,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁你又奶共？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲呢次講得再好 <br />\n都掩蓋唔到佢係害死台灣人既事實"},{"pid":"744098c4a3e2feb31135f8e26446d4a53cdb117c","tid":1414520,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"信佢一成雙目失明啦"},{"pid":"60f887e6664b6104581c17d1b222edb58ce0bd30","tid":1414520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd0f5e7a00cffb72249a2abd82f4a65d7e24e28","tid":1414520,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"唔係小風波咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f16340c4cf38cfa5cf60cbe855566aa891b86d9","tid":1414520,"uid":45761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"見到班友玩國旗,大陸人D愛國心即刻返黎晒啦,仲點會造反"},{"pid":"3c2d95645ed171f3c459fcd54691725674968686","tid":1414520,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"廣州獨立？支那又贏"}]}